summary: Tropical based rock and mountain retexture.
descriptionHtml:
MSFoxhound presents:

Tropical based rock and mountain retexture. I\'ve made a fair colored rock retexture. Slightly volcanic based, all purpose rocks for normal and tropical Skyrim. In addition, it seems very good at Solstheim. Textures at 4096x4096 size, so its for moderate rigs at least. It doesn\'t need any of previous DLC\'s, but it works good with them.

Screenshot are wolcoming gladly!!!

Best regards...
author: MSFoxhound
